data.description: Welcome to this stunning 3-bedroom, 2 full bath, 1 half bath townhouse in the prestigious Manors at Ballenger Creek subdivision. With 2,241 total square feet of living space and a spacious 2-car garage, this home offers the perfect blend of comfort and convenience.  As you step inside, the inviting foyer sets the tone for what awaits you in this modern, beautifully finished townhouse. Ascend the stairs to the open living area, where contemporary design meets cozy comfort. The home boasts stainless steel appliances and elegant granite countertops with a generous island, making it a culinary enthusiast's dream. You'll find a separate pantry closet and ample cabinet space, ensuring all your storage needs are met.  The living room is bathed in natural light, creating a warm and welcoming atmosphere. Adjacent to the living area, you'll discover a convenient powder room, adding to the functionality of this well-planned space.  The third level is dedicated to three spacious bedrooms, with the master bedroom as its centerpiece. The master bedroom features a generously sized walk-in closet, his and hers sink, a roman shower, and a luxurious master suite tub, creating a serene paradise for relaxation.  But the luxury doesn't stop there. The lower level offers a versatile rec room, which can be transformed into a home gym, office, playroom, or anything your heart desires. Head to the back exterior to find the large deck and a private fenced yard, providing a perfect outdoor oasis for entertaining, relaxation, and gatherings. This flexible space has endless opportunities to suit your lifestyle.  The location of this property is truly exceptional. Situated just minutes from Ballenger Creek Park and its scenic trails, you'll have the perfect backdrop for outdoor activities. Additionally, you can easily walk to the nearby Royal Farms and enjoy the convenience of being close to Westview South Shopping Center, Target, TJ Max, Home Depot, Walmart, Chick Fil-A, the Francis Scott Key Mall and much more, all of which are less than 5 minutes away. This townhouse offers not just a home but a lifestyle that combines modern elegance with practicality and accessibility. What's more, its location is a true gem. It's conveniently close to downtown Frederick, offering an array of restaurants, shops, and cultural attractions to explore. You'll find the convenience of having both a Costco and a Sam's Club nearby, each with their own gas station, making errands a breeze.  The property's proximity to Route 15, ICC 270 and Interstate 70 ensures quick access to major transportation routes. If you enjoy scenic drives, you can take the picturesque back roads to Leesburg, adding a touch of adventure to your daily commute. For outdoor enthusiasts, Harper's Ferry is just a short 20-minute drive away, providing endless adventures of hiking, history, and breathtaking views!  Last but certainly not least, the neighborhood is a safe and welcoming community, offering peace of mind and a sense of belonging. This property truly embodies the perfect combination of modern comfort, convenience, and a vibrant lifestyle. Don't miss the opportunity to make it your own!
